OL,3,C'Optical illusion' cycle lane to be
OL,4,Cfixed after people suffer trips and
OL,5,Cfalls
OL,7,FA cycle lane in Keynsham which has
OL,8,Fbeen described as an 'optical
OL,9,Fillusion' will be changed, following
OL,10,Fthe outcome of a road safety report.
OL,12,FKeynsham High Street had been branded
OL,13,F"the most dangerous street in the UK"
OL,14,Fby local councillors, after hidden
OL,15,Fchanges in kerb heights caused a
OL,16,Fnumber of people to trip an injure
OL,17,Fthemselves.
