OL,3,C'Optical illusion' cycle lane to be
OL,4,Cfixed after people suffer trips and
OL,5,Cfalls
OL,7,FBetween March 2022, when the lane
OL,8,Fopened, and November 2023, Bath and
OL,9,FNorth East Somerset Council had
OL,10,Freceivedof people tripping and falling.
OL,12,FThe cycle lane was painted red in
OL,13,FAugust 2023 in a bid to fix the issue,
OL,14,Fbut falls and injuries have continued.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday 21 February, Bath and
OL,17,FNorth East Somerset Council revealed
OL,18,Fthat the lane will now be relined,
OL,19,Ffollowing a road safety audit.
