OL,3,C'Optical illusion' cycle lane to be
OL,4,Cfixed after people suffer trips and
OL,5,Cfalls
OL,7,FThe council has now agreed to replace
OL,8,Fthe solid white line marking at the
OL,9,Fedge of the cycle lane with a broken
OL,10,Fwhite line, to "better delineate it
OL,11,Ffrom the kerb".
OL,13,FIt will also install double yellow
OL,14,Flines adjacent to the kerb between the
OL,15,Fcycle lane and carriageway, which it
OL,16,Fsays should "provide an additional cue
OL,17,Fto pedestrians as they cross the
OL,18,Fhighway".
