OL,7,FThe works will be completed overnight,
OL,8,Fsubject to weather conditions, under a
OL,9,FTemporary Traffic Regulation Notice,
OL,10,Fto avoid disruption to business and
OL,11,Ftraffic during the day.
OL,13,FIn response to the report's outcome,
OL,14,FCouncillor Paul Roper, cabinet member
OL,15,Ffor Economic and Cultural Sustainable
OL,16,FDevelopment, said: "Following the
OL,17,FStage 4 audit report we will carry out
OL,18,Flining work on Keynsham High Street.
